document_data.name: Homfast
document_data.mainbody: '''Homfast''' was a [[Sembia]]n who was alive around [[1188 DR]]. He participated in the discussions with King [[Pryntaler Obarskyr]] in an attempt to acquire the city of [[Marsember]]. The others in his group were [[Kodlos]], Lady [[Threnka]], [[Bennesey]], and [[Jollitha Par]].
